    <div class="container">
        <h1>About SkyWings Airlines</h1>
        <p>
            SkyWings Airlines is committed to providing world-class air travel experiences to our passengers.
            With a fleet of over 200 aircraft, we fly to more than 100 destinations around the world, ensuring safety, comfort, and exceptional service.
            Our mission is to connect people, cultures, and ideas while fostering sustainable aviation practices.
        </p>

        <div class="highlights">
            <div>
                <h3>Global Network</h3>
                <p>
                    Over 100 destinations across 6 continents. Experience the world with SkyWings.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Modern Fleet</h3>
                <p>
                    Our state-of-the-art fleet ensures comfort, safety, and efficiency in every flight.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Customer Satisfaction</h3>
                <p>
                    Ranked among the top airlines globally for customer service and passenger satisfaction.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p>
            Whether you're flying for business or leisure, SkyWings Airlines promises a seamless journey with unparalleled in-flight services, including premium dining, on-demand entertainment, and comfortable seating options.
            We are also committed to minimizing our carbon footprint by adopting cutting-edge sustainable aviation technologies.
        </p>
    </div>

